### ---------------------------------------------------
### 1. Approve University (SUCCESS CASE - Requires GOV Token)
### ---------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/api/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_GOV_TOKEN_HERE>

{
    "universityName": "Global Blockchain Academy"
}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### 2. Attempt Approval as Student (FAIL CASE - 403 Forbidden)
### ---------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/api/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
    "universityName": "Global Blockchain Academy"
}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### 3. Missing Token (FAIL CASE - 401 Unauthorized)
### ---------------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:3000/api/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "universityName": "Global Blockchain Academy"
}